{"id":582816168,"lang":"java","time":"1 month, 2 weeks","timestamp":1636181911,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"8 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/582816168/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"39.7 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int lengthOfLongestSubstring(String s) {\n        if(s.isEmpty()){\n            return 0;\n        }\n        \n        int maxLength = 0;\n        String t = \"\";\n        \n        for(char c:s.toCharArray()){\n            String current = String.valueOf(c);\n            if(t.contains(current)){\n                t = t.substring(t.indexOf(current)+1);\n            }\n            t += current;\n            maxLength = Math.max(maxLength, t.length());\n        }\n        return maxLength;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters"}
